{"tid":1358252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 一鼓網絡勢力正在鼓吹嚴重罪行","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:32:38.000Z","uid":220864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"733cf1d88b040ce5de87397ae5dc92f5cc835a20","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"就係你地呀<br />\n你地知唔知何妖同石鏡泉衰左d咩<br />\n佢兩個on9就係係公開場合講埋d尻野<br />\n又教人用用藤條及水喉通<br />\n又話咩殺到佢片甲不留<br />\n石鏡泉個傻尻可能根本同元朗單野無關<br />\n但係就係佢講埋d on9野<br />\n班人又真係跟住做<br />\n咁咪有位比人入囉<br />\n<br />\n而家你地重係出面係咁講話要勇武燒人祠堂<br />\n咩唔反抗唔得<br />\n屌你咪諗住講下姐<br />\n一陣班鄉黑諗唔開自焚都可以入撚哂我地數<br />\n<br />\n好心你地推到727係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非嘅</span><br />\n目的係比元朗居民感受我地愛香港的<span style=\"color: red;\">熱</span>誠<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">咁屌就算一個唔好彩</span><br />\n個祠堂自己跣低或者自焚<br />\n我地都可以大條道理話白衫同何妖之爭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔撚關我地事</span>"},{"pid":"ba667a9e7f94149c99be51f896d872037d9a008a","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdb662c8d9d1018f719781d9ef6f5122f787171f","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7da9abd9d11c8d2944764eb213bb5c81b4f4bb9a","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"424053116e4cc31d27632eb1f1e2998bf023f15f","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc3fb5b0e5902032fb7f38d57445ca9e0c1f2838","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d540df89758479ec4eeea0404fc0eb6c70133c22","tid":1358252,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de7667d8d359fe7d091fd698cf5de3c5a924ab35","ti